title: BRIEF-WSE Resolves To Exclude From Trading Shares Of Fam and Uniwheels As Of Feb. 20
text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - WARSAW STOCK EXCHANGE (WSE):
* RESOLVED ON THURSDAY TO EXCLUDE FROM TRADING SHARES OF FAM SA AND UNIWHEELS AG AS OF FEB. 20
